snippet.title: Official Call of Duty®: Black Ops III – Eclipse DLC Pack: Zetsubou No Shima Trailer
snippet.description:
Following the events of Der Eisendrache, the Origins heroes find themselves stranded on a remote Pacific island, home to a secret biological research lab experimenting with Element 115. Players will face new terrifying enemies, devastating traps, and classic Zombies side quests to enhance the Origins narrative.

The Eclipse DLC Pack includes four new multiplayer maps — Verge, Rift, Spire, and Knockout — and Zetsubou No Shima, Treyarch’s newest chapter in the Black Ops III Zombies adventure. 

Eclipse is available first on PlayStation 4 on April 19, 2016. Purchase the Call of Duty: Black Ops III Season Pass today: http://bit.ly/BO3SeasonPass
